{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a customizable title section with up to 3 rows of text. Each row needs independent controls for: padding (top, bottom, left, right), spacing between rows, font family, font weight, letter spacing, text transform/case, and text alignment. Include separate desktop and mobile layout sections with identical customization options for both. Organize settings with content inputs separate from typography controls for each row., I need to be able to increase the padding A LOT more, the text needs to be right aligned and in line with the below terms accordion text, so the padding needs to be significant. It might be easier to centre the text, box. Maximum width of 1000px or something (on desktop) but then allow the text to be left / right aligned, Currently all the font is in CAPS, will need the ability to adjust this as well as the letter spacing, font size, weight etc... so if the content boxes can just be text entry boxes and the typography section dictates how that content appears stylisation wise, The row typography section letter spacing doesn't seem to be doing anything. Also need to be able to chose the weight of the typography in each row
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-title-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-title-section__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-title-section__row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-title-section__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}--1 {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.row_1_padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.row_1_padding_bottom }}px;
      padding-left: {{ block.settings.row_1_padding_left }}px;
      padding-right: {{ block.settings.row_1_padding_right }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.row_1_spacing }}px;
      font-family: {{ block.settings.row_1_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.row_1_font.fallback_families }};
      font-weight: {{ block.settings.row_1_font_weight }};
      font-style: {{ block.settings.row_1_font.style }};
      font-size: {{ block.settings.row_1_font_size }}px;
      letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.row_1_letter_spacing }}px;
      text-transform: {{ block.settings.row_1_text_transform }};
      text-align: {{ block.settings.row_1_text_align }};
      color: {{ block.settings.row_1_color }};
    }

    .ai-title-section__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}--2 {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.row_2_padding_top }}px;
